      "name": "Experimental comparison — relative hemolysis index at five operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) compared against in vitro measurements at five flow-speed combinations (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). RH values predicted within 12% of measured values for four of five points; one outlier at 6 L/min/3500 RPM attributed to secondary recirculation zone. Overall model performance deemed acceptable for MRL 2 decision support."
    },
