    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model is fit for purpose to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH acceptance criterion (RH < 1 versus predicate) met across worst-case geometric tolerance combination. Assessment package accepted for regulatory submission support.",
